tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE assessments (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID NOT NULL,
  assessment_date DATE NOT NULL,
  feedback TEXT,
  treatment_effectiveness DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  assessment_id INT,
  response_text TEXT,
  respondent_name VARCHAR(255),
  response_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (assessment_id) REFERENCES assessments(assessment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE treatment_effectiveness (
  treatment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  assessment_id INT,
  effectiveness_score INT,
  improvement_notes TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (assessment_id) REFERENCES assessments(assessment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE assessments (
  assessment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  assessment_date DATE,
  assessment_type VARCHAR(50),
  assessment_score INT
)

CREATE TABLE survey_questions (
  question_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  question_text TEXT,
  question_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  response_text TEXT,
  response_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE treatment_effectiveness (
  treatment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  treatment_type VARCHAR(50),
  effectiveness_score INT
)
CREATE TABLE Assessment ( id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_id INT, assessment_date DATE, assessment_type VARCHAR(50), result VARCHAR(100) );
CREATE TABLE Survey ( id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_id INT, survey_date DATE, satisfaction_level INT, feedback TEXT );
CREATE TABLE Treatment ( id INT PRIMARY KEY, patient_id INT, treatment_type VARCHAR(50), start_date DATE, end_date DATE, outcome VARCHAR(100) );
CREATE TABLE Questionnaire ( id INT PRIMARY KEY, questionnaire_name VARCHAR(100), question_text TEXT );
CREATE TABLE Answer ( id INT PRIMARY KEY, questionnaire_id INT, patient_id INT, answer_text TEXT );
